 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224403693\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022225314\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221719949785\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022234174\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Hi_123\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/2/2024 at 12:49 PM, Hi_123 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre there any mods that add the small things that ksp 2 did in, like kerbals reacting to gravity, the countdown, etc\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat do you mean kerbals \u0022reacting to gravity\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe courage and stupidity stats contribute (I\u0027ve been told) to some RNG combination for facial expressions in situ.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you mean react to G-force. Then yes. In the secondary setting menu.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nESC -\u0026gt; Options Button (Top of ESC GUI) -\u0026gt;\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are tabs on the left that each pertain to either an installed mod or one of the core config pages for the core game. I do not remember if it\u0027s under Basic or Advanced but you can even adjust their G-tolerance with a slider.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hi_123","CreatedById":234174,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-07-06T08:28:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224404544\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022225314\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221720126004\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022227275\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Fizzlebop Smith\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/4/2024 at 9:46 PM, Fizzlebop Smith said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat do you mean kerbals \u0022reacting to gravity\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean, lean backwards and forwards in relation to the G-force\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}